summary: Adds long lost items back to their respective NPCs.
descriptionHtml:
Many things in skyrim are misplaced.... Lost forever, since there is no Lost and Found.... many things are just.... gone forever.... Until now.... Because of this mod, Farengar found his misplaced soul gems, Tolfdir found his favorite book! Farelda found her "stolen" notes! And much more!

Requires Unofficial Skyrim Patch

Fully compatible with The Cutting Room Floor.
author: kvatchcount
